   EDs: Moved Monday in the (a) general news and (l) lifestyle
categories.
</P>
<P>
   ENTERTAINMENT/ARTS
</P>
<P>
   TVSURFER-COLUMN _ ATLANTA _ Highlights of tomorrow's TV viewing.
ETA: 8 p.m. ET.
</P>
<P>
   KELLY-Q-AND-A _ Q&AMP;A with R. Kelly, whose new album is due out
Nov. 10. (SoMurray, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) MOVED.
</P>
