   TRAVEL-SKI-UTAH (Undated) _ It has been called ``champagne
powder'' and ``cold smoke,'' but whatever its name, the snow that
falls on the Utah Rockies is as close to perfect as ski snow gets.
By Tony Chamberlain. 1200 words.
</P>
