from surfers on topics such as the prince's concerns about
architecture, agriculture community regeneration and even religion.
Most of the messages, all of which were at least generally
supportive if not adoring of the prince, were from England, but
there also were a few from Canada and the United States.
</P>
<P>
   The prince, whose popularity has risen since Diana's death, will
review comments, and he might even respond to some of them himself.
</P>
<P>
   ENDIT
</P>
<P>
   Story Filed By Cox Newspapers
</P>
