<P>
   Dried cherries have become increasingly difficult to find
without added sugar and preservatives. But not at CHUKAR CHERRIES.
This company sells Bing, Rainier and Montmorency cherries with
nothing added. The Montmorency are particularly appealing for
people who like a tart-sweet taste. Three one-pound bags are $35.
