sausages are richly perfumed with them. Ooh-la-la. Nine ounces are
$15.95. For a meal later in the day, there is gently smoked and
lightly salted duck breast, which weighs in at about one and a half
pounds ($23.95 a pound).
</P>
<P>
   280 Wilson Avenue, Newark, N.J., 07105; (973) 344-0565 or (800)
