 This ``separate buy'' article is from Latin Trade magazine,
America's leading journal of Latin American business, finance and
trade: &HT;    NEWS AROUND LATIN AMERICA: Pele sets new rules for Brazilian
soccer. Guatemalan Campero chicken has a special recipe for success
_ and beats Kentucky Fried Chicken hands down, say the
connoisseurs. The new daily ``Hoy'' makes a splash in Mexico City _
a town teeming with some 30 other newspapers.
