   Geography: Area, 3.7 million sq. mi.; Capital, Beijing.
</P>
<P>
   Population: 1.22 billion (1997)
</P>
<P>
   Government: Communist Party-led state.
</P>
<P>
   Economy: GDP, $890 billion (1997, exchange rate-based).
</P>
<P>
   Trade: Exports, $182.7 billion; Imports, $142.36 billion (1997).
</P>
<P>
   Currency: Yuan
