   Geography: Area, 2,227 sq. mi., slightly larger than Delaware;
Capital, Bandar Seri Begawan.
</P>
<P>
   Population: 320,000 (1998)
</P>
<P>
   Government: Sultanate
</P>
<P>
   Economy: GDP, $4.9 billion (1997).
</P>
<P>
   Trade: Exports, N/A; Imports, N/A.
</P>
<P>
   Currency: Brunei dollar
</P>
