<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-11-10 19:56 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3900 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NY-AUCTIONS-2TAKES-NY     11-10 0747
