<HEADLINE>
NEELY GIVES US SOMETHING TO FEEL GOOD ABOUT 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By DAN SHAUGHNESSY  
 c.1998 The Boston Globe  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   First John Glenn, now Cam Neely.
</P>
<P>
   What's next? Jim Lonborg on the mound Opening Day at Fenway?
John Hannah leading the blocking for Robert Edwards? John Havlicek
running the fast break for Rick Pitino?
</P>
