<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-11-10 21:58 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4099 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FBC-KEITH-JACKSON-2TA     11-10 0918
